                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><tagsDecl>&amp;renditions;</tagsDecl></encodingDesc></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_ardygæj" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>ardygæj</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>ardigæj</orth><form type="variant"><orth>ardægæj</orth></form></form><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>отсюда</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>from here</q></tr></sense><re><form type="lemma"><orth>ardygæj fæstæmæ</orth></form><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>отныне</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>from now on</q></tr></sense></re><exampleGrp><example><quote>fesæf ardygæj!</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>убирайся отсюда!</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>get out of here!</q></tr></example><example><quote>ardygæj fæstæmæ, zaǧta, næ tyxgænæg basomy kænʒæn myggagmæ tælætyl</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>отныне, сказал он, наш насильник заречется навсегда (думать о) добыче</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>from now on, he said, our rapist will forever renounce (to think about) the prey</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>135</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><exampleGrp><example><quote>fesæf ardygæj!</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>убирайся отсюда!</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>get out of here!</q></tr></example><example><quote>ardygæj fæstæmæ, zaǧta, næ tyxgænæg basomy kænʒæn myggagmæ tælætyl</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>отныне, сказал он, наш насильник заречется навсегда (думать о) добыче</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>from now on, he said, our rapist will forever renounce (to think about) the prey</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>135</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Буквально ‘с этой стороны’. Из <ref type="xr" target="#entry_a"/> ‘этот’ + <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ardæg6i9"/> ‘сторона’ в отложительном падеже, с ослаблением среднего гласного (%iæ%i → %iу%i | %ii%i). См. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_a"/> и <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærdæg"/>; ср. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ardæg6i9"/>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">Literally ‘from this side’. From <ref type="xr" target="#entry_a"/> ‘this’ + <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærdæg"/> ‘side’ in ablative case, with the weakening of the middle vowel (%iæ%i → %iу%i | %ii%i). See <ref type="xr" target="#entry_a"/> and <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ærdæg"/>; cf. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ardæg6i9"/>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>